data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled less than one mile from downtown Hartwell. The privacy fence, hardwood floors, laundry room, office/multipurpose room, and the master suite are just a few notable features of this home. The kitchen boasts a tile countertop and backsplash, bar and a pantry. The fireplace in both the living and dining rooms is a wonderful added bonus for the cold months ahead. The exterior features include covered front and back porches, a carport, paved driveway and a private backyard. Your family will love making this house a home - just 10 minutes from all that Lake Hartwell has to offer.
